# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log

# Environment files
.env
.env.local
```

**3. Structure Your Repository**

Organize it like this:
```
your-project/
├── backend/          # Your Java project
│   ├── src/
│   ├── pom.xml (or build.gradle)
│   └── ...
├── frontend/         # Your frontend folder
│   ├── src/
│   ├── package.json
│   └── ...
├── .gitignore
└── README.md